---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Profil & Sejarah | Isyraq An-Nur Philanthropy">
    <!-- HERO HEADER -->
    <header class="relative h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-royal-950">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544716278-ca5e3f4abd8c?q=80&w=2674&auto=format&fit=crop"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-royal-950 via-royal-950/60 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-4xl px-6 fade-up">
            <span class="text-gold-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-xs mb-4 block">Tentang Kami</span>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display text-white mb-6 leading-tight">Penjaga Tradisi, <br> <span
                    class="italic text-gold-400 font-serif">Pembangun Masa Depan</span></h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-royal-100/80 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
                Isyraq An-Nur adalah perwujudan dari cita-cita luhur untuk mengangkat derajat umat melalui pendidikan yang
                berkarakter, mandiri, dan berwawasan global.
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- SEJARAH (Narrative) -->
    <section id="sejarah" class="py-32 px-6 bg-paper">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-full h-full border-2 border-gold-400/30 rounded-[3rem]"></div>
                    <div class="relative rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-[4/5]">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585036156171-384164a8c675?q=80&w=2670&auto=format&fit=crop"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-1000 transform hover:scale-105">
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-6 bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-slate-100 z-20 max-w-xs transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform">
                        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 font-bold">Didirikan Sejak</p>
                        <p class="font-display text-5xl text-royal-950">1998</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-10">
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-gold-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-3 block">Warisan Nilai</span>
                        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display text-royal-950 mb-8 leading-tight">Akar Sejarah & Perjuangan</h2>
                        <div class="prose prose-lg text-slate-600 font-sans leading-relaxed">
                            <p class="mb-6">
                                Bermula dari sebuah rumah wakaf sederhana, Yayasan Isyraq An-Nur memulai langkahnya dengan memberikan hak pendidikan bagi mereka yang kurang beruntung, terutama anak-anak yatim dan dhuafa.
                            </p>
                            <p class="mb-6">
                                Niat tulus untuk mencetak generasi yang tidak hanya cerdas intelektual namun juga kokoh secara spiritual menjadi pondasi utama kami. Seiring waktu, amanah umat semakin besar, menuntut kami untuk terus bertransformasi.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Kini, Isyraq An-Nur terus berinovasi mengembangkan kurikulum terpadu yang memadukan tradisi klasik dengan sistem modern, memastikan setiap lulusan memiliki daya saing global tanpa kehilangan akar nilai-nilai keislaman.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-10 border-t border-slate-200 pt-10">
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-5xl font-display text-gold-600 block mb-2">1.2k+</span>
                            <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold">Alumni Tersebar</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-5xl font-display text-gold-600 block mb-2">100%</span>
                            <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold">Lulusan Kompeten</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- VISI & MISI (Cards) -->
    <section id="visi" class="py-32 bg-royal-950 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none"
            style="background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/arabesque.png');"></div>

        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
            <div class="text-center mb-20">
                <span class="text-gold-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-xs mb-4 block">Tujuan Kami</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display text-white">Visi & Misi Strategis</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gold-400 mx-auto mt-6 rounded-full"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
                <!-- Visi -->
                <div class="md:col-span-1 bg-white/5 p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition duration-500 group">
                    <div
                        class="w-16 h-16 bg-gold-400 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-royal-950 mb-8 shadow-xl shadow-gold-400/20 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                        <i data-lucide="eye" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-display mb-6 text-gold-400">Visi Utama</h3>
                    <p class="text-royal-100/90 leading-relaxed font-light text-lg italic">
                        "Menjadi pusat kaderisasi ulama dan intelektual muslim yang mandiri, berakhlak mulia, dan
                        berwawasan global."
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Misi -->
                <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-white/5 p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition duration-500">
                    <div
                        class="w-16 h-16 bg-royal-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-royal-950 mb-8 shadow-xl shadow-royal-100/20">
                        <i data-lucide="target" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-display mb-8 text-white">Misi Strategis</h3>
                    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                        <div class="flex gap-5 group">
                            <span class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-2xl group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300">01</span>
                            <p class="text-royal-100/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">Menyelenggarakan pendidikan Islam yang memadukan tradisi klasik (Turats) dan sains modern.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-5 group">
                            <span class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-2xl group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300">02</span>
                            <p class="text-royal-100/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">Mengembangkan unit usaha produktif untuk mendukung kemandirian ekonomi yayasan dan santri.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-5 group">
                            <span class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-2xl group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300">03</span>
                            <p class="text-royal-100/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">Membekali santri dengan keterampilan digital, teknokratis, dan jiwa kepemimpinan Islam.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-5 group">
                            <span class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-2xl group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300">04</span>
                            <p class="text-royal-100/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">Menyebarkan dakwah yang moderat dan inklusif (Rahmatan lil 'Alamin) melalui media kreatif.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PIMPINAN (Leadership) -->
    <section id="pimpinan" class="py-32 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-20">
                <span class="text-gold-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-xs mb-3 block">Kepemimpinan</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display text-royal-950 leading-tight">Dewan Pengasuh & Pengurus</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 text-center">
                <!-- Kyai -->
                <div class="group">
                    <div class="relative w-56 h-56 mx-auto mb-8">
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-gold-400 rounded-full rotate-12 group-hover:rotate-45 transition duration-700">
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full h-full rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-2xl relative z-10 overflow-hidden bg-slate-100">
                             <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506794778202-cad84cf45f1d?q=80&w=400&auto=format&fit=crop"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-700 transform group-hover:scale-110">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-royal-950 mb-2">KH. Ahmad Bisri, Lc. MA</h3>
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-gold-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">Pengasuh Utama</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 px-4 leading-relaxed font-light italic">"Pendidikan adalah kunci pembuka pintu surga dunia dan akhirat melalui ilmu yang bermanfaat."</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Direktur -->
                <div class="group">
                    <div class="relative w-56 h-56 mx-auto mb-8">
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-royal-200 rounded-full rotate-12 group-hover:rotate-45 transition duration-700">
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full h-full rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-2xl relative z-10 overflow-hidden bg-slate-100">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?q=80&w=400&auto=format&fit=crop"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-700 transform group-hover:scale-110">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-royal-950 mb-2">Dr. H. Muhammad Ilham</h3>
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-gold-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">Direktur Pendidikan</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 px-4 leading-relaxed font-light italic">"Inovasi dalam pendidikan Islam adalah keniscayaan untuk menjawab tantangan zaman modern."</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Kepala Yayasan -->
                <div class="group">
                    <div class="relative w-56 h-56 mx-auto mb-8">
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-royal-200 rounded-full rotate-12 group-hover:rotate-45 transition duration-700">
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full h-full rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-2xl relative z-10 overflow-hidden bg-slate-100">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?q=80&w=400&auto=format&fit=crop"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-700 transform group-hover:scale-110">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-royal-950 mb-2">H. Yusuf Mansur, SE</h3>
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-gold-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">Ketua Yayasan</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 px-4 leading-relaxed font-light italic">"Kemandirian ekonomi umat dimulai dari pengelolaan wakaf dan donasi yang profesional."</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FASILITAS -->
    <section id="fasilitas" class="py-32 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-100">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center md:items-end mb-16 text-center md:text-left">
                <div class="mb-8 md:mb-0">
                    <span class="text-gold-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-xs mb-3 block">Lingkungan Belajar</span>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-display text-royal-950">Fasilitas Penunjang</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-4 max-w-xl font-light">Menciptakan ekosistem yang kondusif bagi pertumbuhan intelektual dan spiritual setiap santri.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 hover:text-royal-950 hover:border-royal-950 transition cursor-pointer">
                        <i data-lucide="chevron-left" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 hover:text-royal-950 hover:border-royal-950 transition cursor-pointer">
                        <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
                <!-- Fasilitas 1 -->
                <div class="group relative rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden aspect-[4/5] shadow-xl">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541888946425-d81bb19240f5?q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-700 group-hover:scale-110">
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-royal-950 via-royal-950/40 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-8 transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500">
                        <div class="w-10 h-1 bg-gold-400 mb-4 rounded-full"></div>
                        <h4 class="text-white font-display text-xl">Asrama Eksklusif</h4>
                        <p class="text-royal-200/70 text-xs mt-2 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Kapasitas 500+ Santri</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Fasilitas 2 -->
                <div class="group relative rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden aspect-[4/5] shadow-xl">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505664194779-8beaceb93744?q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-700 group-hover:scale-110">
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-royal-950 via-royal-950/40 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-8 transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500">
                        <div class="w-10 h-1 bg-gold-400 mb-4 rounded-full"></div>
                        <h4 class="text-white font-display text-xl">Perpustakaan Digital</h4>
                        <p class="text-royal-200/70 text-xs mt-2 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Akses Kitab & Jurnal</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Fasilitas 3 -->
                <div class="group relative rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden aspect-[4/5] shadow-xl">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516321318423-f06f85e504b3?q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-700 group-hover:scale-110">
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-royal-950 via-royal-950/40 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-8 transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500">
                        <div class="w-10 h-1 bg-gold-400 mb-4 rounded-full"></div>
                        <h4 class="text-white font-display text-xl">Lab Riset Al-Khawarizmi</h4>
                        <p class="text-royal-200/70 text-xs mt-2 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Pusat Multimedia</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Fasilitas 4 -->
                <div class="group relative rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden aspect-[4/5] shadow-xl">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1625246333195-58197bd47d26?q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-700 group-hover:scale-110">
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-royal-950 via-royal-950/40 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-8 transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500">
                        <div class="w-10 h-1 bg-gold-400 mb-4 rounded-full"></div>
                        <h4 class="text-white font-display text-xl">Greenhouse Wakaf</h4>
                        <p class="text-royal-200/70 text-xs mt-2 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Laboratorium Alam</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

